name: Fog Installation: Lost Smoke
description:
The diamond plate represents the past hard work and stress from construction jobs.
The fog represents all the hits of marijuana I have taken in my life. 
2021/2022 I ended up in a new era where I no longer have to work construction jobs anymore and this reflects all the blood, sweat, tears that went into working in the trenches and being under paid. Born in the mud to the glo up.
